{"tid":991632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為打擊謠言 WhatsApp限制同一訊息最多轉發5次","createTime":"2019-01-22T13:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T14:06:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"df1c39a2b5bb8a9742c8e4dcf2de569bcdf2ab8e","tid":991632,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"為打擊錯誤資訊和謠言廣傳，WhatsApp周一（21日）表示，由當日起將會限制全球的WhatsApp用戶轉發短訊次數，每個短訊最多只能轉發5次。WhatsApp將在同日開始更新程式，預料Android用戶將會首先收到更新通知，iOS的用戶將緊隨其後。<br />\n<br />\n公司的政策及通信部副總裁格朗（Victoria Grand）當日宣布此消息。WhatsApp用戶此前可向20個群組或個人轉發短訊，不過隨着印度有WhatsApp用戶去年轉發有人綁架孩童的虛假消息，導致該國有民眾遭其他人執行私刑殺死後，WhatsApp遂於去年7月在印度實施有關措施。<br />\n<br />\n目前WhatsApp在全球擁有15億用戶，公司一直想辦法阻止用戶濫發錯誤資訊和謠言。外界一度憂慮，用戶能夠透過WhatsApp傳播假新聞、假圖片等惡作劇，而無法追尋真正來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/為打擊謠言-whatsapp限制同一訊息最多轉發5次-022616202.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%82%BA%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80-whatsapp%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E8%BD%89%E7%99%BC5%E6%AC%A1-022616202.html&d=AqY7y7jJ%2FuWEOQGpCgMhpzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5297e29b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/為打擊謠言-whatsapp限制同一訊息最多轉發5次-022616202.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca2a7567f84e0d0ca94d28395252c202696bb657","tid":991632,"uid":216817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01b3fabd004c41f2a74cfdd3e3d2eb4751445991","tid":991632,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca2a7567f84e0d0ca94d28395252c202696bb657","tid":991632,"uid":216817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"好重要就直接打電話啦"},{"pid":"ee75c174f53a9b14a26cd24f68bb8bf0833b272e","tid":991632,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"治標不治本，我要轉發copy and paste都做到